{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e0212ec3-94e8-4da4-8ce0-6f9e851a76b0","content":"Here are two reliable programmatic approaches:\n\n## 1. Query MSBuild properties (best for CI)\n\nCreate a minimal MAUI project (or use your existing one) and query the properties directly:\n\n```bash\ndotnet new maui -n Probe --no-restore\ndotnet msbuild Probe/Probe.csproj -t:_ResolveAndroidSdkPath \\\n  -getProperty:AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion \\\n  -getProperty:AndroidSdkCommandLineToolsVersion \\\n  -getProperty:AndroidDefaultTargetDotnetApiLevel \\\n  -getProperty:AndroidLatestStableApiLevel\n```\n\nThese properties are set by the `Microsoft.Android.Sdk` workload pack and reflect the exact versions your SDK expects.\n\n## 2. Inspect the workload pack directly\n\n```bash\n# Find your dotnet root\nDOTNET_ROOT=$(dirname $(readlink -f $(which dotnet)))\n\n# The Android SDK pack props declare all requirements:\ncat \"$DOTNET_ROOT\"/packs/Microsoft.Android.Sdk.*/*/AutoImport.props\n# or look in:\nfind \"$DOTNET_ROOT/packs\" -path '*Microsoft.Android.Sdk*' -name '*.props' \\\n  | xargs grep -h \"AndroidSdk\\|ApiLevel\"\n```\n\nThe key properties you'll find:\n\n| Property | Meaning |\n|----------|---------|\n| `AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion` | e.g. `34.0.0` |\n| `AndroidSdkCommandLineToolsVersion` | e.g. `11.0` |\n| `AndroidDefaultTargetDotnetApiLevel` | Target API (e.g. `34`) |\n\n## Using it in CI\n\n```bash\n# Install exactly what the SDK needs:\nAPI=$(dotnet msbuild YourApp.csproj -getProperty:AndroidDefaultTargetDotnetApiLevel -nologo)\nBT=$(dotnet msbuild YourApp.csproj -getProperty:AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion -nologo)\nCT=$(dotnet msbuild YourApp.csproj -getProperty:AndroidSdkCommandLineToolsVersion -nologo)\n\nsdkmanager \"platforms;android-$API\" \"build-tools;$BT\" \"cmdline-tools;$CT\"\n```\n\nThis way your CI always stays in sync with whatever MAUI workload version is installed — no hardcoding.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2784e7f0-1f81-4210-83dd-4b3352c1eaf5","outputTokens":584,"requestId":"A850:77FDA:681563:7851B8:69FBE31F"},"id":"f4f86262-6c84-4b05-81bb-fa044f119216","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:56:12.078Z","parentId":"9d11597b-b430-478d-86d5-463428fd0c3b"}
